Home Made Rose Water 🌹 

Ingredients:
1. Paneer Rose Petals
2. Water

Procedure: In a big steel vessel, keep a base like stone or iron stand and place a small size steel bowl on top of it. Around the small size bowl, add the petals and pour a half cup of water on the petals. Close the Vessel with a glass lid and cover the air hole with chappathi dough. Pour a little water on the middle of the lid to help the vapour to drip in the small size steel bowl. We can collect the rose water till the petal colour gets faded.

Fact: From 1kg of rose petals, i could collect only 74ml of rose water🥲

Note: Store it in fridge and use it for a month

Charcoal Face Pack🖤

Ingredients: Just an used coconut shell & Lemon juice to cleanse it

Procedure: Burn the Used coconut shell after drying in sun for atleast 2 days. Cool it down immediately by soaking in the water. Add one full lemon to cleanse it in the same bowl. Sun dry the washed burnt coconut shells and powder it

Frozen Gel for face💚

Ingredients:
1. Ladies Finger
2. Water

Procedure: Chop the ladies finger and soak it overnight in a cup of water. Filter it and transfer the gel to an ice cubes tray. This frozen gel ice cubes can be stored for a week. Use it minimum thrice a week to see a better result
